data.description: Come discover tranquility in this 3-bed, 2.5-bath home on 3/4 acre with an extra 3 bedrooms. 9-foot ceilings and an adorable loft with a computer nook await. Outside, enjoy the pool, dog run, and expansive grounds. With 3 extra rooms,create your own personalized touch. This 22-year-old home is attractively priced adequately for a swift sale. Unlock the potential of this timeless gem, with ample space to craft your vision. Also, it features fresh paint throughout the home!!
